* The emon1-monitor catches the Kalpha-peaks, and emon2 the Kbeta peaks.
*
* %Example: Test_source_lab Detector: emon1=8.80276e+14
* %Example: Test_source_lab Detector: emon2=2.34884e+14
*
* %Parameters
*
* %Link
*
* %End
